            <div class="process-step blue">
                <div class="process-step-header">
                    <p>05</p>
                    <h3>Deliver your Power Shortlist</h3>
                </div>
                <p>You won’t just get resumes. You’ll get context. Each recommendation includes in-depth insights,
                    assessment results, and our perspective on why they’re the right fit, for the role, the culture, and
                    your long-term goals.</p>
